N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 65.16 - Place of filing

State Regulations

Unless filing electronically or otherwise directed, an
original and three copies of any paper required under these rules must be filed
at the Board's principal office in Albany, New York. Electronic filings do not
require any copies to be filed and are to be filed at the location designated
by the Board. Notes
